headline: Q4 Earnings Outperformers: Monster (NASDAQ:MNST) And The Rest Of The Beverages, Alcohol, and Tobacco Stocks
summary: As the craze of earnings season draws to a close, here’s a look back at some of the most exciting (and some less so) results from Q4. Today, we are looking at beverages, alcohol, and tobacco stocks, starting with Monster (NASDAQ:MNST).
